hoppscoch

**Status code**
200 ->OK
404 ->Not found   
400 ->Bad request
500 ->Internal server error

**Add Information in URL**
*Query string* 
https://www.google.com/Search?q=harry+potter
?name=shraddha&marks=95

*Adding variable*
:id or :num or :q or {{id}} or <id>   //it means that id is a variable and we should pass a value in this variable like:-
https://api.potterdb.com/v1/movies/:id      it means we have to replace with value of id like:-  https://api.potterdb.com/v1/movies/2b9c2188-0961-491b-916e-43d0ec3d0948



